<text top="686" left="313" width="241" height="9" font="font6" id="p1_t105" reading_order_no="102" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">(FBS) under an atmosphere of humidified air containing</text>
<text top="698" left="313" width="241" height="10" font="font6" id="p1_t106" reading_order_no="103" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">5 % CO 2 . In the experiments in which the effect of estro-</text>
<text top="709" left="313" width="241" height="9" font="font6" id="p1_t107" reading_order_no="104" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">gen was studied, the medium was replaced with phenol</text>
<text top="721" left="313" width="241" height="9" font="font6" id="p1_t108" reading_order_no="105" segment_no="15" tag_type="text">red-free DMEM and 2 mM glutamine (Nissui</text>
